# .kontxtignore
# Add glob patterns (one per line) to exclude files from kontxt processing.
# Lines starting with # are comments.
# Built-in defaults are included below. You can add more entries at the end.

**/node_modules/**
**/.git/**
**/.cursor/**
**/.vscode/**
**/.idea/**
**/.DS_Store/**
**/bun.lock
**/bun.lockb
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/.gitattributes
**/.kontxt/**
**/.kontxtignore
**/dist/**
currentWork.md

